  Safety, Compliance, and Risk Management: Establish and rigorously enforce world-class operational safety standards and procedures, particularly those related to high-speed signaling systems (e.g., ETCS Level 2). The expert ensures strict compliance with all national and international rail regulations and manages operational risk assessments.
